      "acceptanceCriteria": "Richardson extrapolation with GCI < 1% on hemolysis index QoI across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "GCI computed on pressure and velocity fields; hemolysis index GCI computed at only 2 of 5 operating points and exceeds 2% at high-flow condition. Achieved level 2."
