      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions (inlet velocity profile, fluid viscosity, hematocrit) match CFD boundary conditions within 2% across all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles in experiments were spatially averaged; CFD used uniform inlet. Hematocrit deviation up to 4% at two operating points. Achieved level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric (e.g., E_rel) applied to hemolysis index with uncertainty bands from both experiment and simulation overlapping at all operating points.",
      "rationale": "Relative error computed but experimental uncertainty not formally propagated. Simulation uncertainty from Monte Carlo not combined with experimental measurement uncertainty in a single comparison metric. Achieved level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
